Package: edgestream
Type: Package
Title: Streaming (Dynamic) Graph Analytics
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2026-07-14
Authors@R: person(given = "bagol1000", family = "developer", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "01199218@pw.edu.pl")
Description: Maintains graph metrics incrementally as edges arrive in a stream.
    Provides an in-memory dynamic graph with incremental connected components
    (Union-Find), triangle counting, clustering coefficients, degree tracking,
    neighbourhood queries, edge weights, edge removal, PageRank, strongly
    connected components and approximate betweenness, backed by a 'C++17' core
    with 'OpenMP' support. Node IDs are 0-indexed.
